{"tid":2024092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做愛方面youtuber同娛樂圈體育界係唔係一樣?","createTime":"2020-05-19T11:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T00:52:12.000Z","uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2146abd69acdfbffca4bf861ce875ae360aa2e8","tid":2024092,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"娛樂圈<br />\n陳冠希羅志祥<br />\n<br />\n體育界<br />\n2016年美國媒體「E！News」得到里約奧運內部人士透露，選手村裡的「戰況」非常激烈，有些人在比賽後才好好享受「性愛派對」，有些則是在練習期間就要來一發：「性愛可以幫助我拿金牌！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然近年來奧運主辦單位都會提供超過10幾萬個保險套，但總是供不應求，例如2012年倫敦奧運，主辦單位準備了15萬個保險套，去年的里約奧運更是破紀錄達到45萬個！<br />\n<br />\n據美國知名體育頻道ESPN於2012年倫敦奧運熱潮時的報導，「我覺得70&ndash;75%的選手都在比賽期間有過性行為。」美國游泳名將羅切特（Ryan Lochte）曾這樣說。"},{"pid":"d6bfcdef5e965ba08851388ff7f63d1becd94117","tid":2024092,"uid":9566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"有權力地位既人都係"},{"pid":"f63ee8e04828d69984fe76c1d700f7f761b2d266","tid":2024092,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6bfcdef5e965ba08851388ff7f63d1becd94117","tid":2024092,"uid":9566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"有權力地位既人都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"咁呢樣當然"},{"pid":"f8553bd27260198c0ebd6dc6ec2a4f9406b349ba","tid":2024092,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63ee8e04828d69984fe76c1d700f7f761b2d266","tid":2024092,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6bfcdef5e965ba08851388ff7f63d1becd94117","tid":2024092,"uid":9566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"有權力地位既人都係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"咁呢樣當然"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"好撚葡萄牙????<br />\n我有方法幫到你喎~"},{"pid":"9c475090dd644257a7b4343248c384a813218904","tid":2024092,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8553bd27260198c0ebd6dc6ec2a4f9406b349ba","tid":2024092,"uid":